{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now the mood, as I said, was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After about-- I'm not sure-- an hour, between an hour or two, going very slowly, the train had to stop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Couldn't see a station, but somebody stood on some luggage, looked across the other wall, looked outside, and he must have seen somebody, you know, a uniformed man in, you know, with perhaps the insignia of a-- you know somebody working in a nearby station, at a railway.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sort of-- sort of gestured where we would go, for instance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, couldn't shout, because we didn't know if he had guards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't see any guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know if-- if we had and if something good happened, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway, from the distance, the man made-- gave this sign, we were told.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now obviously, when we were-- when he stepped off his luggage and told us, our mood immediately changed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then my father and I, you know, we had sort of like a discussion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Vielleicht it was only [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Vielleicht-- maybe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm speaking German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Vielleicht.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Maybe it was only on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe-- you know, maybe he knows something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Train's going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Who knows what.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Never heard of again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But probably he knew more than we.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, so the mood was bad, and in the evening we reached-- it was a very slow train-- we reached a town called Gliwice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now I sort of make a couple of remarks which I have not made in my book because I only learned about it later.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When Hitler wanted to start the war, he sent some soldiers, I think in Polish uniform.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, he starteed an incident in that particular town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's a border town.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
